comment: /**  * Retrieve the current script source text as String.  * @return the script text  * @throws IOException if script retrieval failed  */
code: /**  * Retrieve the current script source text as String.  * @return the script text  * @throws IOException if script retrieval failed  */ String getScriptAsString() throws IOException.

comment: /**  * Indicate whether the underlying script data has been modified since  * the last time {@link #getScriptAsString()} was called.  * Returns {@code true} if the script has not been read yet.  * @return whether the script data has been modified  */
code: /**  * Indicate whether the underlying script data has been modified since  * the last time {@link #getScriptAsString()} was called.  * Returns {@code true} if the script has not been read yet.  * @return whether the script data has been modified  */ boolean isModified().

comment: /**  * Determine a class name for the underlying script.  * @return the suggested class name, or {@code null} if none available  */
code: /**  * Determine a class name for the underlying script.  * @return the suggested class name, or {@code null} if none available  */ @Nullable String suggestedClassName().
